  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduo a LXDE Common</title>

    <para>
      The <application>LXDE Common</application> package provides a set of default
configuration for LXDE.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Informao do Pacote</bridgehead>
